section.p:
It could have accommodated five passengers if Loki hadn’t extended the storage area to provide room
                    for various pieces of high-tech wireless communications equipment and supplies. This was, after all,
                    his mobile base of operations for running the one-man Stormbringer faction.

“Damn me, we haven’t.” He extended his hand and nearly crushed hers with it. “Aldous Morris Johnston;
                    I’m fortunate to be senior legal counsel for several companies backing Operation Exorcist.” He
                    turned to the servant. “Get us a pot of coffee and some finger sandwiches in here.”
